{
  "texts": [
    "Currently, a topic that has captured the attention of the scientific community is the environment (Sébastien et al. 2009; Pamucar et al. 2022; Jaung 2022; Branca et al. 2023; Tlili et al. 2023).",
    "Sébastien et al. (2009) have studied how to develop biodiversity in the Metaverse to improve the user experience.",
    "On the other hand, Jaung (2022) has conducted research on the demand for forest recreation, reaching the conclusion that virtual experiences were preferred over real experiences in nature.",
    "Furthermore, the Metaverse has the potential to enhance the environment by minimizing the production of physical goods and instead focusing on digital creations.",
    "This approach can result in reduced pollution, lowered risk of contamination, and the prevention of harmful waste generation that negatively impacts the environment (Branca et al. 2023; Tlili et al. 2023)."
  ]
}